Actress-cum-comedienne Helen Paul aka Tatafo has addressed ladies cohabiting with men. The stand-up comedian advised them to change their status to ‘married on credit’. “Ladies, if you are living with a man that hasn’t paid your bride price, change your status to “Married on credit,” she wrote.   Fuji musician Easy Sawaba is dead     I’m blessed to have inner, outer beauty – Regina…     Love, lies kept me with ex-lover, says Tonto Dikeh   She informed her husband they are officially ‘married on credit’ because her pride price is due for renewal as the former has since expired. “Oya o…. @femi_bams come and pay o…. Una Ekiti money don expire o…. We are now officially married on credit,” the mother of four wrote.